title: Mercedes NTG4 v10  2012
description:
Version 10.0 (2012) navigation map update disks for W204 C and GLK class with the COMAND-APS navigation system. Released may 2012 This is for COMAND NTG4 and not for the NTG4.5 system fitted from Model Year 2011 onwards. 

The 2011/2012 version covers the whole of Western Europe.
The navigation data on the 2011/2012 version covers almost 9.2 million kilometres of road throughout Europe. 

Compatibility:
C-Class (>03/07)
GLK-Class (>10/08)
SLS (>03/10)
